This paper deals with indexing techniques for improving query performance in data warehouses, which is a core topic in the field of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also mentions frequent itemset mining, which is a common technique in data mining and machine learning (cs.DS, cs.AI). The use of indexing for query optimization is also related to information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper presents an automatic method for index selection, which involves machine learning and optimization techniques (cs.LG).
